rows.label: bf10060100_0010
rows.name: It's been a while, "Father"...

rows.label: bf10060100_0020
rows.name: Logos...

rows.label: bf10060100_0030
rows.name:
Is that my real name?
What's it mean, "Logos"?

rows.label: bf10060100_0040
rows.name:
It has no meaning. All it represents
is the ego of those who named you.

rows.label: bf10060100_0050
rows.name:
Hah...
How many years has it been...?

rows.label: bf10060100_0060
rows.name:
I forget.
It has been far too long...

rows.label: bf10060100_0070
rows.name: You know why I'm here, don't you?

rows.label: bf10060100_0080
rows.name:
I know it all. All that you experience
is passed on to me here.

rows.label: bf10060100_0090
rows.name: ...Then let's get straight to the point.

rows.label: bf10060100_0100
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hngh-?!

rows.label: bf10060100_0110
rows.name: No need to rush, my child.

rows.label: bf10060100_0120
rows.name:
I am fading.
I'll be gone...soon enough...

rows.label: bf10060100_0130
rows.name: Is that right...?

rows.label: bf10060100_0140
rows.name: Then I'll take it all.

rows.label: bf10060100_0150
rows.name:
Do as you wish.
If you believe that is your role...

rows.label: bf10060100_0160
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10060100_0170
rows.name: Is that choice really "mine"?

rows.label: bf10060100_0180
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10060100_0190
rows.name:
Answer me.
This is what I came to hear.

rows.label: bf10060100_0200
rows.name: ...It is a choice you made together.

rows.label: bf10060100_0210
rows.name: Good answer.

rows.label: bf10060100_0220
rows.name: Thanks for creating me.

rows.label: bf10060100_0230
rows.name: Ah, and here comes the other answer...
